            "description": "Creates a new user account.\n\n**Method**: `POST`  \n**Endpoint**: `{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register`\n\n**Purpose**  \nRegisters a new user using the provided account details.\n\n**Required body fields**\n\n- `username`: Unique username for the account\n    \n- `email`: User email address\n    \n- `password`: Account password\n    \n- `name`: Full name of the user\n    \n\n**Example request body**\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"username\": \"plantlover99\",\n  \"email\": \"testuser@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\",\n  \"name\": \"Jane Doe\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n**Response overview**\n\n- **Success**: Returns a successful registration response when the account is created.\n    \n- **Error**: May return an error if required fields are missing, invalid, or if the user already exists."
          },
          "response": []
        },
